Subject: [PATCH] drm/amd/display: Add Null check for DPP resource
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.6.3
Git-commit: e186400685d8a9287388a8535e2399bc673bfe95

commit e186400685d8a9287388a8535e2399bc673bfe95 upstream.

[what and why]
Check whether dpp resource pointer is null in advance and return early
if so.

